    "12240209": {
      "title": "Risk of hepatobiliary and pancreatic cancers after hepatitis C virus infection: A population-based study of U.S. veterans",
      "abstract": "Background ::: HCV may increase the risk of hepatopancreaticobiliary tumors other than hepatocellular carcinoma (HCC). Previous case-control studies indicated a possible association between HCV and intrahepatic cholangiocarcinoma (ICC). Little is known about the association between HCV and extrahepatic cholangiocarcinoma (ECC) or pancreatic cancer."
